# Complex disclosed relationship test data
# Tests combinations of discovered features (shared addresses/phones) with
# disclosed relationships (REL_ANCHOR/REL_POINTER) to exercise match keys
# that combine both discovered and disclosed components.
#
# Data sources: COUNTY_MARRIAGES, COUNTY_DIVORCE_FILINGS
