#   - Marriage record discloses HUSBAND/WIFE relationship (two-way disclosure)
#   - Expected: match key combining +ADDRESS+PHONE+REL_POINTER(HUSBAND:WIFE)
#
# Scenario 2: Same couple in divorce filings
